@startuml
title "User Sign Up"
actor User #green
App -> User: Presents Initial screen for sign up/sign in
User -> App: Provides details for the user account creation
App --> AppServer: Sends the collected data over the internet 
database Database
AppServer --> Database: User is created and details are stored in the database
AppServer --> App: Response from the AppServer
App -> User: Succesful creation of User Account or Error if any
@enduml
